race.description: Let Us Impressu Print Group Maiden Plate
race.comment: GLACIELE (5) was well in the betting on debut but just ran into a couple better on that occasion. Will have taken benefit from that race day experience and where there's smoke there's fire. Looks the one they all have to run down. HE IS THE KISS (1) has had plenty of chances but has placed seven of 14 over this sprint trip and has also hit the frame on all going. Can play a role in the outcome. ON THE THRONE (7) is facing the starter for the first time but has shown some ability at the trials and won't need to be a superstar to be competitive against this lot. Respect any market moves. The well-related AINSLEY (8) (half to G3 winner and 2xG2 placed Single Bullet) will strip fitter second-up from the break and maps ideally from gate three. In the mix. OKANUI (6) best of the rest with the 3kg claim.
